First you will need to create an image from your Workpress machine
To create an image highlight the ec2 instance to go Image and press create image. It will take several minutes to create an image
Now you can create ec2 instanace usign thsi image
Be sure to assign this instance to another AZ (in Advansed settings)
Now when incatnace is started create a Applicaiton Load balaning with inctances: Web server 1 and Web server 2.
Put test.html on each server so you can see on which server you are
The DNS will be created for the loadbalancer - you can access your HA Web servers now with this DNS name.
